
Friend's Influence: Ever notice how your friends' posts introduce new ideas or trends?
Heroes and Trends: We often follow trends because our heroes or admired figures do.
Sticking to Comfort: Social media can keep us in our comfort zone, preferring familiar ideas.
Excitement of Popularity: Viral posts or trending topics catch our attention and excitement.
Sharing for Connection: Sharing our thoughts or trends helps us feel connected, like chatting with friends.
